                        <interp inst="t18480403-1173-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value=""></interp>NOT GUILTY</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Common Serjeant.</hi>
               </p>
